{"tid":1588321,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關於護港神獸「鶳」一字讀法嘅小小建議","createTime":"2019-09-22T18:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T04:50:27.000Z","uid":90207,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"959fbc87cc898b90119154937ee5a83b80b35f53","tid":1588321,"uid":90207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"中文豆知識：<br />\n中文字向來一字一音，但原來亦有例外。「瓩」這個字，一個字有兩個音，讀作「千瓦」，是中文字裡極少數一字有兩音的字。<br />\n近日香港出現護港神獸，名字叫「鶳」，好奇查了字典，這個「鶳」就讀作「獅」，簡單易記。不過，為了重視這隻護港神獸的崛起與重要性，雖然名字只有一個字，但賦予這個字新讀音「獅鳥」並普及開去，以一字二音來彰顯其意義，似乎更佳。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cc8fcc2e17ff3ae855daacd6f9b83f03cf1fa8","tid":1588321,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"3ed102122cde2e14dc36fca290daa97fe3066434","tid":1588321,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bce592098344645ef120ba922ee86338c13c17f","tid":1588321,"uid":189652,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T19:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f73fb18d3c65470a29adaf2f884029bdebbc411","tid":1588321,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e256151f9d3a66200b01f8c895bc5be2df7e539","tid":1588321,"ui